# SOW Builder - Form Design Specifications

## Overview
This document provides detailed specifications for designing the SOW Builder UserForm in Microsoft Word VBA. The form is structured as a multi-page wizard with navigation controls to guide users through the process of creating a Statement of Work document.

## Form Layout
- **Form Caption**: "SOW Builder"
- **Width**: 600 points
- **Height**: 500 points
- **Position**: Center Owner
- **Background Color**: System background
- **Border Style**: Fixed Dialog
- **Control Box**: Yes (with minimize/maximize buttons)

## Common Controls (Visible on All Pages)
- **Navigation Buttons**:
  - btnBack: Position (420, 460), Width: 80, Height: 24, Caption: "< Back"
  - btnNext: Position (505, 460), Width: 80, Height: 24, Caption: "Next >"
  - btnGenerate: Position (505, 460), Width: 80, Height: 24, Caption: "Generate"
  - btnCancel: Position (15, 460), Width: 80, Height: 24, Caption: "Cancel"

- **Progress Indicator**:
  - lblProgress: Position (200, 460), Width: 200, Height: 20, Caption: "Page X of 4"

## Page 1: Client Information
- **Frame**: fraPage1
  - Position: (15, 15)
  - Width: 570
  - Height: 430
  - Caption: "Client Information"

- **Controls**:
  - lblDate: Caption "Date:", Position (30, 30)
  - txtDate: Position (150, 30), Width: 140
  
  - lblContactName: Caption "Contact Name:", Position (30, 60)
  - txtContactName: Position (150, 60), Width: 200
  
  - lblCompanyName: Caption "Company Name:", Position (30, 90)
  - txtCompanyName: Position (150, 90), Width: 200
  
  - lblAddress1: Caption "Address Line 1:", Position (30, 120)
  - txtAddress1: Position (150, 120), Width: 250
  
  - lblAddress2: Caption "Address Line 2:", Position (30, 150)
  - txtAddress2: Position (150, 150), Width: 250
  
  - lblWTWParty: Caption "WTW Contracting Party:", Position (30, 180)
  - cmbWTWParty: Position (150, 180), Width: 200, DropDownStyle: 2 - Dropdown List
  
  - lblClientName: Caption "Client Legal Name:", Position (30, 210)
  - txtClientName: Position (150, 210), Width: 200
  
  - lblStartDate: Caption "Start Date:", Position (30, 240)
  - txtStartDate: Position (150, 240), Width: 140
  
  - lblEndDate: Caption "End Date:", Position (30, 270)
  - txtEndDate: Position (150, 270), Width: 140

## Page 2: Compensation Options
- **Frame**: fraPage2
  - Position: (15, 15)
  - Width: 570
  - Height: 430
  - Caption: "Compensation Options"

- **Controls**:
  - fraCompOptions: Position (30, 30), Width: 250, Height: 180, Caption: "Select Compensation Option"
  - optA: Position (45, 50), Caption: "Option A: Fee Only"
  - optB: Position (45, 80), Caption: "Option B: Fee + Commission"
  - optC: Position (45, 110), Caption: "Option C: Fee Offset by Commission"
  - optD: Position (45, 140), Caption: "Option D: Commission Only"
  
  - lblAnnualFee: Position (310, 40), Caption: "Annual Fee:"
  - txtAnnualFee: Position (380, 40), Width: 140

  - fraBillingOptions: Position (310, 80), Width: 230, Height: 100, Caption: "Billing Options"
  - optMilestone: Position (325, 100), Caption: "Milestone Billing"
  - optInstallments: Position (325, 130), Caption: "Regular Installments"

