## Visibility Management
- On form initialization:
  - Only fraPage1 is visible
  - btnBack is disabled
  - btnGenerate is not visible (only shown on last page)
  
- When Option A (Fee Only) is selected:
  - fraBillingOptions is visible
  - fraCommissionDetails is not visible
  
- When Option B or C is selected:
  - fraBillingOptions is visible
  - fraCommissionDetails is visible
  
- When Option D (Commission Only) is selected:
  - fraBillingOptions is not visible
  - fraCommissionDetails is visible

## Control Navigation
- btnNext: Increases page number, shows next frame
- btnBack: Decreases page number, shows previous frame
- btnGenerate: Visible only on the last page, calls document generation
- btnCancel: Unloads the form without creating a document

## Data Validation
The form should implement validation for:
- Required fields (Client name, contact, dates)
- Numeric-only inputs for fees and commission percentages
- Valid date formats
- Policy list validation (at least one policy for options B, C, and D)
